### Version

v20.13.1

### Platform

Darwin 23.3.0 Darwin Kernel Version 23.3.0

### Subsystem

_No response_

### What steps will reproduce the bug?

Use the code sample mentioned in the [official documentation](https://nodejs.org/en/learn/asynchronous-work/understanding-setimmediate):
```javascript
const baz = () => console.log('baz');
const foo = () => console.log('foo');
const zoo = () => console.log('zoo');

const start = () => {
  console.log('start');
  setImmediate(baz);
  new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
    resolve('bar');
  }).then(resolve => {
